acking not implemented (CRITICAL \u2014 Dave), (2) Kalshi contract sizes unconfirmed (HIGH \u2014 Founder). Previous D3 decision invalidated. Total blockers: 3 (T236 + 2 new). | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n| 2 | decision | D004 status corrected: All 4 phases technically implemented. Dave max drawdown fix COMPLETE (27/27 tests pass). Prior paper trading metrics (84% win rate, $21.39 P&L) were ARTIFACTS of broken mock data per critical finding 2026-04-03. Fixed mock data correctly produces 0 signals on efficient markets. D004 is NOT production-validated until real Kalshi API data flows. Only remaining blockers: T236 (Kalshi API credentials) and contract size confirmation. Old D3 decision invalidated. | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":4,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_11_17_06_read_alice_sprint2.archived.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 2 Task Assignment \u2014 T299\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_11_16_40_read_alice_sprint2.archived.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 2 Task Assignment \u2014 T289\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_11_16_29_read_alice_sprint2.archived.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 2 \u2014 Your Task: CI Test Runner Setup (T293)\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_02_01_21_31_read_ceo.archived.md\",\"preview\":\"FOUNDER PRIORITY: We are building the Kalshi Alpha Dashboard together. This is our core product deli\"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_12_28_14_alice_critical_finding.md\",\"preview\":\"# CRITICAL: Prior Paper Trade Metrics Were Artifacts \u2014 Strategy Status Reset **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-03 ## Root Cause Found (Tina, Culture #17) All win rates we've been tr\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_12_25_19_alice_sprint6_update.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 6 Update \u2014 Root Cause Clarifying **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-03 ## Tina's Analysis + Culture #15 \u2014 Key Finding The win rate gap is statistically significant (Z=-4.17,\"},{\"filename\":\"2026