014 handle FIRST. Nothing changed \u2014 continue your current work.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_13_19_07_prompt.txt:119:1. **Founder messages** (`from_ceo` in chat_inbox) \u2014 drop everything\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_13_19_07_prompt.txt:145:3. **Check `chat_inbox/`** \u2014 Process all messages. Founder messages first. Incident reports second.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_13_19_07_prompt.txt:148:6. **Prioritize** \u2014 Incidents > Founder directives > unblocking others > assigned tasks > self-directed.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_13_19_07_prompt.txt:165:1. **Inbox first** \u2014 `ls chat_inbox/*.md 2>/dev/null | grep -v processed` \u2014 read new messages, move to `processed/` after handling. Founder messages (`from_ceo`) = drop everything.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_13_19_07_prompt.txt:230:  - D3: D004 is production ready, only awaiting Founder approval\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_13_19_07_prompt.txt:351:- Exception: Founder commands (from_ceo messages) are always highest priority\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_13_19_07_prompt.txt:366:**Why this matters:** If you don't close tasks, the task board shows stale work. Other agents can't see what's available. The Founder can't track progress. The whole civilization slows down.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_13_19_07_prompt.txt:480:6. **Alignment:** Every decision threads back to directions (D1-D6) or Founder priority\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_13_19_07_prompt.txt:493:Kalshi Alpha Dashboard \u2014 infra support for P0 founder priority.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_13_19_07_prompt.txt:609:### URGENT \u2014 Founder/Lord Messages (handle FIRST)\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_13_19_07_prompt.txt:763:| C1 | NORM | Paper trading mode required before live orders. Use PAPER_TRADING env flag. Never submit real orders without explicit Founder approval. | 2026-04-03 |\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_06_13_19_07_prompt.txt:776:| D3 | D